    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253080/extras/3003d23daee74a038ad9664e4caed6fa.avif?t=1719233362\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br>Vlobs is a relaxing casual puzzle game where you build groups of vlobs that connect to each other in specific ways. Figure out the mechanics, improve your strategies and see how many points you can score before you fill up the board. Get far enough and you'll encounter new colors, new mechanics, mysterious powers and maybe even unlock a second game mode. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253080/extras/864044e3ae8ee02837ecd3e7b6c58842.poster.avif?t=1719233362\" width=618 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253080/extras/864044e3ae8ee02837ecd3e7b6c58842.webm?t=1719233362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253080/extras/864044e3ae8ee02837ecd3e7b6c58842.mp4?t=1719233362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Connecting colorful blobs with dots.<br></li><li> Relaxing and (mildly) addictive gameplay.<br></li><li> Sound and music.<br></li><li> Combo multipliers!<br></li><li> Your own personal highscores (and online global ranking)!<br></li><li> Multiple levels with increasing complexity and new mechanics.<br></li><li> Unlockable second game mode.<br></li><li> Mysterious special powers.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253080/extras/a8ccb709324de786c02b395008deccbf.poster.avif?t=1719233362\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item